---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section id="personal-shopper" class="relative py-24 bg-[#111111] overflow-hidden w-full border-t border-white/5">
    
    <div class="absolute left-10 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden xl:block">
        <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[1.2em] text-white/5 rotate-90 inline-block origin-center whitespace-nowrap">
            Asistencia Global de Compras
        </span>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-16">
            
            <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left" data-aos="fade-right">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                    <span class="h-px w-8 bg-gold/40"></span>
                    <span class="text-gold font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[9px]">Servicio Externo</span>
                </div>
                
                <h4 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-white font-black italic mb-8 leading-tight pr-12">
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Asesoría de</span> <br class="hidden md:block"> Compras
                </h4>
                
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-md mb-10 italic pr-2">
                    ¿Desea adquirir piezas en portales internacionales? Nuestro equipo gestiona sus compras en Amazon, Alibaba y Shein con la rigurosidad de nuestra casa de moda.
                </p>

                <a href={`${base}/asesorias`} class="group inline-flex items-center gap-6 text-white text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] font-black transition-all">
                    <span>Conocer el Servicio</span>
                    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-gold group-hover:w-20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-sm" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="relative p-5 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02]">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574634534894-89d7576c8259?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" 
                         alt="Personal Shopper Forever One" 
                         class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000">
                    
                    <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-12 h-12 border-t border-r border-gold/30"></div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-12 h-12 border-b border-l border-gold/30"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute -bottom-16 -right-10 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
        <span class="text-[15rem] font-serif font-black text-white italic pr-20">FO1</span>
    </div>
</section>
